<div class="cases">

  <h2>Cases</h2>

<p>Explore hundreds of cases and documents <!--files--> from the Circuit Court for the District of Columbia, <!--the Maryland and Virginia state courts--> the Maryland state courts, and the U.S. Supreme Court. <!--We have annotated selected case files with explanatory narratives and commentaries to situate the case in law and history.--> Currently the project contains only petitions for freedom cases originating in the D.C. Circuit Court sitting in Washington, D.C., between 1800-1859.</p> 

<h3>Petitions for Freedom</h3>

<p>Enslaved individuals made a variety of claims in order to support their freedom petitions. Browse the Petition for Freedom cases by the claims for freedom made by the parties involved. Many cases contain more than one claim to freedom.</p>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-8">
         <!-- Browse by Claims -->
         <%= form_tag doc_dropdown_path do %>
         <% select_tag :claims, options_for_select(@claims_facet), :prompt => "Select Claim for Freedom Made", :class => "custom-dropdown__select", :onchange => "this.form.submit();" %>
         <% end %>
        </div>
        </div>

    </div>
  </div>

<h3>Explore Cases and Documents</h3>

<p>We have annotated selected case files with explanatory narratives and commentaries to situate the case in law and history. Case Files include all documents related to a petition case even if the case went to another court on appeal. Case Documents include all documents in all cases and can be browsed by document type, court term, or location.</p>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">

      <!-- Start cases -->
      <h4>Case Files</h4>

      <div class="list-group">
        <%= link_to "Explore Annotated Cases", casesAnnotated_path, class: "list-group-item"  %>
        <%= link_to "Explore All Cases", casesAll_path, class: "list-group-item" %>        
      </div><!-- /list group-->
      <!-- End cases -->

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">Jurisdiction</div>
        <div class="col-md-8">
         <!-- Browse by Jurisdiction -->
         <%= form_tag doc_dropdown_path do %>
         <% select_tag :jurisdiction, options_for_select(@jurisdiction_facet), :prompt => "Select Jurisdiction", :class => "custom-dropdown__select", :onchange => "this.form.submit();" %>
         <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <br/>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">Outcome</div>
        <div class="col-md-8">
          <!-- Browse by Outcome -->
          <%= form_tag doc_dropdown_path do %>
          <% select_tag :outcome, options_for_select(@outcome_facet), :prompt => "Select Outcome", :class => "custom-dropdown__select", :onchange => "this.form.submit();" %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div><!-- /column-->

    <div class="col-md-6">

      <!-- Start documents -->

      <h4>Case Documents</h4>
      <div class="list-group">
        <%= link_to "Explore All Documents", documents_path, class: "list-group-item" %>
      </div><!-- /list group-->

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">Document Type</div>
        <div class="col-md-8">
          <!-- Browse by Document Type -->
          <%= form_tag doc_dropdown_path do %>
            <% select_tag :document, options_for_select(@subCategory_facet), :prompt => "Select Document", :class => "custom-dropdown__select", :onchange => "this.form.submit();" %>
          <% end %>
          <!-- End documents -->
        </div>
      </div>

      <br/>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">Term</div>
        <div class="col-md-8">
         <!-- Browse by Term -->
         <%= form_tag doc_dropdown_path do %>
         <% select_tag :term, options_for_select(@term_facet), :prompt => "Select Term", :class => "custom-dropdown__select", :onchange => "this.form.submit();" %>
         <% end %>
       </div>
      </div>

      <br/>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">Location</div>
        <div class="col-md-8">
          <!-- Browse by Places -->
          <%= form_tag doc_dropdown_path do %>
          <% select_tag :places, options_for_select(@places_facet), :prompt => "Select Location", :class => "custom-dropdown__select", :onchange => "this.form.submit();" %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div><!-- /column-->
  </div><!-- /row-->
</div><!-- /cases-->


